{"hash":"20b9a8dd94a07529a40814d09af92c709137098a","data":{"post":{"id":"9543354211148769f08efeca4b160b84","title":"[HackerRank] Grid Search","category":"알고리즘","series":0,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://www.notion.so/image/https%3A%2F%2Fs3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com%2Fsecure.notion-static.com%2F9d41c1ed-b707-4925-a36b-726cc66c7341%2Fhacker-rank-logo.png?table=block&#x26;id=62d1f9a2-d7ad-4c7e-bb71-ee02ff10d667&#x26;width=3260&#x26;userId=&#x26;cache=v2\"></p>\n<br>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/the-grid-search/problem\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">The Grid Search</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"intro\"><a href=\"#intro\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Intro</h2>\n<p>다중 반복밖에 떠오르지가 않았다.</p>\n<p>예전에 풀었던 문제중에 <code class=\"language-text\">BFS</code>와 비슷한 느낌이 들어서</p>\n<p>비슷하게 접근해봤지만 잘 풀리지 않아서 결국 반복문으로 접근했다.</p>\n<p>테스트 케이스를 다 통과하긴 했지만...</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-solve\"><a href=\"#how-to-solve\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>How To Solve</h2>\n<p>2중 배열이라서 2중 반복을 통해 전체 숫자를 방문했다.</p>\n<p>여기서 대상이 되는 패턴을 찾을 때 또 2중 반복을 하게되면</p>\n<p>4중반복문이 된다는 생각에 다르게 접근해봤다.</p>\n<p>크기를 이미 알고 있으므로 <strong>index</strong>를 이용하여 <code class=\"language-text\">while</code>문으로 한개씩 검증했다.</p>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"solution\"><a href=\"#solution\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Solution</h2>\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">gridSearch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\"><span class=\"token constant\">G</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">P</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> r <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">G</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">length</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> c <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">G</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">length</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> gr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">P</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">length</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> gc <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">P</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token property-access\">length</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">grid</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">i<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> j</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token arrow operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> head <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> pi <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> pj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> di <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> i\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> dj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> j\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>head <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span> gr <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> gc<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">G</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>di<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>dj<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token constant\">P</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>pj<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token constant\">P</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>pi<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>pj <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          pi<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n          pj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>\n          di<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n          dj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> j\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          pj<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n          dj<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n      head<span class=\"token operator\">++</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> r <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> gr<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;=</span> c <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> gc<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> j<span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">G</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token constant\">P</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">grid</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> j<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">'YES'</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">'NO'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<hr>\n<br>\n<h2 id=\"reference\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Reference</h2>\n<span class=\"reference\">\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/akasai/Algorithm-Solutions/blob/master/HackerRank/Implementation/32.The_Grid_Search.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Github</a></p>\n</span>\n","tags":[{"title":"Algorithm","path":"/tag/Algorithm/"},{"title":"HackerRank","path":"/tag/HackerRank/"},{"title":"Javascript","path":"/tag/Javascript/"}],"date":"9월 17 목, 2020","update_date":"9월 17 목, 2020","timeToRead":1,"headings":[{"depth":2,"value":"Intro","anchor":"#intro"},{"depth":2,"value":"How To Solve","anchor":"#how-to-solve"},{"depth":2,"value":"Solution","anchor":"#solution"},{"depth":2,"value":"Reference","anchor":"#reference"}]},"related":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Add Two Numbers","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem Solving / Algorithm","path":"/lc-add-two-numbers/","date":"2020.10.13"}},{"node":{"title":"[Leetcode] Merge Two Binary Tree","category":"알고리즘","description":"Leetcode / Problem